VSQLite++ - A welldesigned and portable SQLite3 Wrapper for C++

Overview:
  1. Instructions for POSIX Systems
  2. Instructions for Windows Systems with Visual C++

Requirements:
- boost 1.33.x (headers only)
- GCC/G++ 3.4.x and higher or Visual C++ 8/2005

1. Instructions for POSIX Systems

- Edit 'options.py' if boost is not available through /usr/include
- run ./build.sh

Installation is not implemented at the moment. Building only. 
Library output is copied to ./libs
Include ./vsqlite++/include for build

